commitResults.messageTitle: Add JUnit tests for LoanDataManager parsing and I/O
commitResults.messageBody:
Added LoanDataManagerTest to verify:
- Correct serialization and sanitization in formatRecord()
- Accurate parsing of repaid and non-repaid loans from file lines
- Handling of malformed or invalid records
- Round-trip integration with DataManager's writeToFile(),
  appendToFile() and tryLoad()
- Ensures LoaDataManager reliably persists and restores Loan objects
  from text file
